{"tid":1909903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"年青地盤工被控元旦襲警 控方指便衣警「傷勢嚴重腦有瘀血，需放五星期病假」","createTime":"2020-03-04T09:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T10:21:32.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"492b1d2f91971c0dc86cf3e657a21934d8b9cea3","tid":1909903,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:42:26.000Z","msg":"今年元旦當晚，示威者在旺角設路障堵路，有便衣警跟蹤示威者時被發現遭圍毆。警方事後拘捕多人，日前再多一人被控，案件今於觀塘裁判法院提訊。據悉，案中受傷警員傷勢嚴重，腦內有瘀血，傷勢影響其進食及行路，需放五星期病假。辯方則指被告的招認並非自願作出。<br />\n...<br />\n據悉，當晚案發地點有約十名黑衣示威者正在堵路。警員A跟隨觀察，突然被指「影人相」，眾人向警員叫囂。警員A表露身份，遭眾人包圍，被告與另外兩名早前已被起訴的男子涉襲擊警員A，其中一人拉警員A落地，打其背部再拳打他，另有人以膝跪警員A的頸。而本案被告則被指踢警員A。<span style=\"color: red;\">警員受傷，一度暈倒幾分鐘</span>。<br />\n<br />\n控方透露，<span style=\"color: red;\">警員A傷勢嚴重，腦內有瘀血，傷勢影響其進食及行路，需放五星期病假</span>，情況至2月中始好轉。<br />\n...<br />\n署理主任裁判官張潔宜批准被告以現金5,000元與女友的人事擔保5,000元保釋，其間須守宵禁及每周向警署報到一次。<br />\n【案件編號：KTCC268/20】<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200304/LILU3YRH5ECBRSUFHCDJYPMKQI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200304%2FLILU3YRH5ECBRSUFHCDJYPMKQI%2F&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=b7dbf80f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200304%2FLILU3YRH5ECBRSUFHCDJYPMKQI%2F&h=f2ed73cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200304/LILU3YRH5ECBRSUFHCDJYPMKQI/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76365c0813316c987dd9866f330304d68997a9fe","tid":1909903,"uid":29982,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:44:53.000Z","msg":"即係重行得? 不完美,可接受,需改善"},{"pid":"1fa881bb852f82c237892d1a29bd61a5635add42","tid":1909903,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:45:57.000Z","msg":"呃病假仲咁大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43382bc3b14a64d35dcca2d9dede711418b3b29","tid":1909903,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:47:04.000Z","msg":"冒警撚執勤唔SHOW 委任証, 明人打就屈鳩人襲警 ?<br />\n對付恐怖分子,  冇斷手斷腳仲有條命已經要偷笑了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.facebook.com/fans.hkgolden/videos/454600148528214/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffans.hkgolden%2Fvideos%2F454600148528214%2F&h=c8b898fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b0c95ac52f625f6f05bac75bcaca4a5b8551cee","tid":1909903,"uid":264387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T10:02:49.000Z","msg":"有曬片見到#A406捉完人之後自己冧低㗎喎，咁撚樣都呃5星期假"},{"pid":"e1ebd4e0426ecd4cd642ac61bf2e68c129a12f4f","tid":1909903,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T10:21:32.000Z","msg":"到底大家撐唔撐港台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1909951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1909951</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}